              </author>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīgoviṃdabhagavatpūjyapādaśiṣyaparamahaṃsaparivrājakāvāryaśrīśaṃkarācāryabhagavataḥ kṛtaṃ muṃḍakopaniṣadbhāṣyaṃ [?]m // (f. 27).</colophon>
